    <string name="message_help">
        <![CDATA[
        To search the lexicon, tap the magnifying glass icon. You can use either Greek characters or
        <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beta_code#Encoding">Beta code</a> to search.
        Diacritics are optional in both cases. For example, you can search for λόγος by typing
        \"logos.\" Search queries are not case sensitive.
        <br><br>
        To switch between modes, open the navigation drawer by swiping in from the left edge of
        the screen or tapping the application icon in the upper-left corner.
        ]]>
